Titolo: Legends of Dawn

Anno: 2013

Descrizione: Legends of Dawn is a single-player open world role-playing video game developed by the Croatian developer Dreamatrix Game Studios and published by Valve via their digital distribution platform Steam. It was released worldwide on 27 June 2013 for Microsoft Windows. Set within a fictional world of Narr, which spans several continents, the player is free to explore and progress at his own pace.